WEBVTT

00:00.554 --> 00:04.318
Evsei, a black and white spaniel, waits patiently...

00:04.446 --> 00:07.337
...as kids gather around to pet him every day.

00:08.107 --> 00:11.305
He's part of a dog therapy session in eastern Ukraine...

00:11.717 --> 00:14.887
...where canines help children adjust to a life after war.

00:15.671 --> 00:20.794
Evsei is one of 28 dogs at a humanitarian aid center in Zaporizhzhia...

00:21.203 --> 00:26.168
...where children also draw, sing nursery rhymes and receive psychological support.

